{"tid":746071,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【突發】蔡少芬冇啦啦送生日禮物畀張晉","createTime":"2018-07-17T09:35:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-05T10:07:33.000Z","uid":48905,"like":8,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"faae5bab73cb0921fe46dd5d9e96959a2005c2b5","tid":746071,"uid":48905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T09:35:38.000Z","msg":"藝人蔡少芬（<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">Ada</span>）同老公張晉向來恩愛非常，呢日張晉就喺社交網上載一家四口去玩嘅短片，片中見到Ada一家喺唔同地方留倩影，有啲去咗沙漠亦有去咗水上樂園，不論係佢哋兩公婆定係同囡囡一齊玩，睇到都覺得溫馨！張晉仲Tag咗太太話：「成街人都睇死佢開公司，仲開戲畀你拍呀！咁多聯絡架？唔洗講野啦我地。」而Ada亦都話：「係呀，係以前．．．以前．．．費事嘈呀．．．」網民都話呢段片紀錄咗佢哋一家人快樂時光，簡直係佢哋美好回憶，有網民話都唔係Ada同張晉生日，點解會係講係生日禮物呢？"},{"pid":"ca1d77f5ce42b138536573fde740c8a40b5dfbf8","tid":746071,"uid":17545,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T10:02:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 比比竟然唔貼百萬生日會張圖 你唔貼果張圖講Ada老公生日嚟把撚啊？"},{"pid":"c445e5b0ee588911a822da09ae276c7ff89b329b","tid":746071,"uid":48905,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"ca1d77f5ce42b138536573fde740c8a40b5dfbf8","tid":746071,"uid":17545,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T10:02:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 比比竟然唔貼百萬生日會張圖 你唔貼果張圖講Ada老公生日嚟把撚啊？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T10:05:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/17/180459_6c94f2478c5ba860cc8bc7105cb87ce0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F17%2F180459_6c94f2478c5ba860cc8bc7105cb87ce0.png&h=82e62d80&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/17/180500_3aa33010e239ac25d372974c9a1d5c42.